[5] Hong Kong CHP updates: 13 Apr 2014, 14 Apr 2014: 10th imported case. Hong Kong ex Guangdong
Dates: Sun 13 Apr 2014 and Mon 14 Apr 2014
Source: Hong Kong Centre for Health Protection (CHP) [edited]
http://www.chp.gov.hk/en/content/599/34345.html (13 Apr 2014)
